verses.verse: Halleluya. O prayse the LORDE in his Sanctuary, prayse him in the firmament of his power.
Prayse him in his noble actes, prayse him in his excellet greatnesse.
Prayse him in the sounde of the trompet, prayse him vpo the lute and harpe.
Prayse him in the cymbals and daunse, prayse him vpon the strynges and pype.
Prayse him vpo the welltuned cymbals, prayse him vpon the loude cymbals.
Let euery thinge yt hath breth, prayse the LORDE. Halleluya.
